poemContent:
Ermm, excuuuse me
Frau briee
Herr Fischer
Buzzards in the sea


Serum Goo and Slime, locker 253
Now i'm in line, trousers clean,
`Stop making that stuuupid voice`!
erm, what are you doing boys?
Promoting this, promoting that
on shiny targets a lokki shat
Screaming out, he made a fuss
Stomp'd a bee infront of a bus!

ei ei ei
bzzzzzz
nah, that's g-
